Semantic 
https://semantic-ui.com/

Semantic is a development framework that helps create beautiful, responsive layouts using human-friendly HTML.

https://github.com/doabit/semantic-ui-sass
gem 'semantic-ui-sass'

# add to rails5
1) add to gem file "gem 'semantic-ui-sass'"
2) it needs jquery so add in gemfile "gem 'jquery-rails'"
3) bundle install
4) create file app/assets/stylesheet/custom.css.scss and add "@import 'semantic-ui';"
5) добавить:
// Loads all Semantic javascripts
//= require jquery
//= require semantic-ui
в app/assets/javascript/application.js